29:57.162 --> 30:01.733 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN (through translator): Inside
the Mexican
communities, people go to work
with fear.

30:01.767 --> 30:05.303 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the kids' grades can go down
