30:10.475 --> 30:16.415 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: In response to
those fears,
Mexican Foreign Secretary
Claudia Ruiz Massieu

30:16.448 --> 30:19.251 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
