Mexico's consul
generals.

30:19.284 --> 30:24.389 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They urge the five-plus million
undocumented
Mexicans in the U.S. to stay
calm.

30:24.423 --> 30:28.326 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CLAUDIA RUIZ MASSIEU, Mexican
Foreign Secretary:
We are alert.

30:28.360 --> 30:37.102 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That is why I have instructed my
50 consulates
to increase their outreach to
our community.

30:37.135 --> 30:40.906 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Massieu says she
wants to work
with the incoming
administration, but she

30:40.939 --> 30:45.310 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
