through on all
his promises, it's not only
Mexico that would

30:45.343 --> 30:47.079 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
be harmed.

30:47.112 --> 30:51.183 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CLAUDIA RUIZ MASSIEU: If the
environment were
to become more hostile, I'm sure
the United

30:51.216 --> 30:59.257 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
States would also feel a
negative effect in
its economy, in prices,
inflation, in loss

30:59.291 --> 31:03.962 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of jobs, and in loss of people
that really
contribute a lot to different
communities

31:03.995 --> 31:05.764 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
throughout the United States.

31:05.797 --> 31:10.602 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: But even before
Trump's taken
office, illegal immigration has
risen, as

31:10.635 --> 31:14.272 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
has the panic among Mexicans on
both sides
of the border.

31:14.306 --> 31:23.181 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
For the "PBS NewsHour" I'm Nick
Schifrin in
Ciudad Juarez, Mexico.

31:23.215 --> 31:30.021 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Stay with us.

31:30.055 --> 31:34.459 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
